cu.explanation_en: Setting MCC to 0 (invalid) causes PLMN configuration rejection, preventing network registration and cell attachment.

du.explanation_en: Setting PRACH message 1 frequency start to -1 causes frequency misalignment, leading to RACH failure and UE connection issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PRACH 訊息 1 頻率起始設定為 -1 會導致頻率錯位，造成 RACH 失敗和 UE 連線問題。
